  <brief_title>A Study to Evaluate the Effectiveness and Safety of RXI 109 on the Outcome of Revised Hypertrophic Scars</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open-Label, Multi-Center, Prospective, Within-Subject Controlled, Phase 2a Study to Evaluate the Effectiveness and Safety of RXI 109 on the Outcome of Scar Revision Surgery for Hypertrophic Scars in Healthy Adults</official_title>
